Class Rule

  • java.lang.Object
    • datalog.Rule

  • public class Rule
extends java.lang.Object
    This is a class for representing a datalog rule.
    The Explanation of Rule is based on this example:
    C(?y):- A(?x,?y),B(?z,?y),?y=2.
